<div id="c1">
<p>One of the best explanations of Gödels incompleteness theorem can be found in Douglas R. Hofstadter&#8217;s &#8220;Gödel, Escher, Bach: an Eternal Golden Braid&#8221;. The book is highly recommended and really a piece of art itself.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://amix.dk/">amix</a>
