<div id="c2">
<p>I don&#8217;t think that characterization of the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vienna_Circle" rel="nofollow">Vienna Circle</a> is very accurate. Read the Wikipedia for a better description of their philosophical positions.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by ThomasW
 on February 12, 2007 <a href="godel#c2" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
